raw_text = "~ start
## 10am
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Mabel: Morningggg babe 🥱
Player: Morning Mabes
Mabel: img: mabel/185
Mabel: Behold, zombie Mabel!
- Did you sleep at all??
	Player: Did you sleep at all?
	Mabel: Whats \"sleep\" 😵‍💫
	Player: You look totally worn
	Mabel: I feel worn
- Not the usual PJs?
	Player: Not the usual PJs?
	Mabel: Oh uhm... 😅
	Mabel: Y-yeah this is just some PJs the Sorority gave me
	Mabel: Free clothes r-right?? Haha
	Player: Guess so
Mabel: I think I got like three hours
Mabel: Thought: They seriously wouldn't stop..
Mabel: Thought: Sleeping in pink panties and not my usual PJs was kind of icky too
Mabel: But I'm fiiine! Just had a lot on my mind
Mabel: I have a presentation so I'm a bit stressed about it I guess 😅
Player: Sure?
Mabel: Thought: I don't want to worry him
Mabel: Mhmm! Don't worry!!
Mabel: I always pull through 💪
if Story.has_flag(\"LOVE\"):
	Mabel: Ooh our uhm... \"sorority queen\" said she wants me to show up for a Friday evening meet and greet with other new members 🫣
	Mabel: For some reason, she thinks I'm perfect for this event
	Mabel: Are you gonna be there babe? 🤭
	Mabel: They said some of the newer members of the frat house are going to show up too
	Mabel: So it got me thinking 👀
	Player: I didn't get that msg but I'll check with the group!
	Mabel: Please doo 😙 It would be nice to see you hehe
	Mabel: We could cozy up and chat ☺️
	Mabel: Thought: But I hope I won't be dressed so strangely this time
Mabel: I'm srsly so yawny 🥱
Player: Make sure you catch up on sleep soon
Mabel: Yes yes, a full cat nap is due! Meow! 🐱
Mabel: Okay lemme just get up and get dressed, brb
Mabel: And NOW I can't even decide what to wear ugh 😩
Mabel: I wish you were here to tell me what to wear 🤭
Player: Would you like that?
Mabel: Mhmm!
Mabel: I think some girls might not like being told what to wear but
Mabel: I just love being able to dress up for you hehe 🥰
Player: Sounds good! I don't mind
Mabel: We'll do it when I'm ready hehe 😌
Mabel: Buuut today I'm wearing something safe cause of zombie form Mabel
if Story.has_flag(\"LUST\"):
	do advance_time(0, 5)
	Mabel: Brb for now 🫠
	Mabel: Thought: Maybe I'll ask on Social hehe
	do social_post(\"mabel_whattowear\")
	Mabel: Thought: oh! There's a comment already
	Mabel: Thought: It's that guy that took my Social..
	Mabel: Thought: He's looking at my sorority picture too?? Those weren't even meant for
	Mabel: PinkThought: Is he peeping on me???
	Mabel: Thought: That's it, I'm blocking him this time for real
	Mabel: Thought: The button isn't there??
	Mabel: Thought: My sorority account won't even let me block boys!?
	Mabel: Thought: So he just gets to... keep watching me?
	Player: Still deciding on the outfit? 😄
	Mabel: Uh haha, yeah! Indecisive disaster!!
	Mabel: Thought: He wants to walk me home after class...
	Mabel: Thought: I gotta run home quickly, before he spots me
	Mabel: That's me 😅
Mabel: Oh I gotta rehearse too
Mabel: I'll just grab something and run before I'm late
do social_post(\"mabel_walk_to_class\")
Mabel: img: mabel/186
Mabel: And wish me luck on my presentation!!
Player: You got this Mabes 😉
Mabel: 🩷
Mabel: Talk later!
=> END
"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
